    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-09-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-09-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="531" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d531">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Bolet Peraza</persName>
                                to Mr. <persName type="to">Foster</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Venezuela</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">New
                                        York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-09-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 21,
                                    1892</hi>
                        </date>. (Received September 21.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The acquittal of Gonzales does not disprove charge that the vessel <hi rend="italic">South Portland</hi> is armed to be used against my
                            Government. I urge the libelling of the vessel. Will you so direct and
                            detain her? If you require it will personally visit you and present my
                            proofs to-morrow. Please answer by telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">N. Bolet Peraza.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
